      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this specimen\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior\u2014has been maintained to an uncompromising standard. This is an exemplary opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that mirrors its original showroom delivery state. Performance is seamless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance history and absolute mechanical integrity.",
