    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely stunning shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that perfect, 'like-new' experience without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
