    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, completely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery still carries that new-car scent, with no visible wear on the bolsters or stitching. Every technological feature, from the crystal-clear infotainment display to the multi-zone climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by factory-trained technicians. The sale includes a comprehensive binder of service history, two sets of original keys, and the unused factory floor mats. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the assembly line. Non-smoker, no pets, and only hand-washed using professional-grade products.",
      "price": 43500.0,
